title: Result: Cambuur, ADO Den Haag draw in Eredivisie
text:
Result: Cambuur, ADO Den Haag draw in Eredivisie Â© Getty Images Mike Havenaar's goal is cancelled out by Furdjel Narsingh as Cambuur draw 1-1 with ADO Den Haag. Filed: Sunday, October 25, 2015 at 13:41 UK Last Updated: Sunday, October 25, 2015 at 13:41 UK 
Cambuur and ADO Den Haag have played out a 1-1 draw in the Eredivisie. 
In a quiet first half, Sander van de Streek 's strike was saved by Martin Hansen . 
The Den Haag goalkeeper was called into action again when Martjn van der Laan's long-range effort was saved. 
The match came to life at the start of the second half when Mike Havenaar gave Den Haag the lead with a shot into the bottom right corner. 
Furdjel Narsingh equalised just four minutes later when he found the bottom right corner. 
Timothy Derijck nearly won the match for Den Haag in the final minute but Leonard Nienhuis kept the score level.
